=== 人道主義援助 ===
{{See also|{{Internal link helper/en|Crisis mapping|Crisis mapping}}|聰明行動族|{{Internal link helper/en|Ushahidi|Ushahidi}}}}

在2010海地大地震後兩天，OpenStreetMap和Crisis Commons的志愿者使用衛星映像在OSM補充了海地Port-au Price區域的道路、建築物和避難營的标记，後來更使OSM成爲「最齊全的海地數位地圖」。<ref name="nytimes">{{cite news |title=Digital Help for Haiti |url=http://gadgetwise.blogs.nytimes.com/2010/01/27/digital-help-for-haiti/ |newspaper=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]] |date=2010-01-27 |accessdate=2014-04-15 |language=en |archive-date=2017-10-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171011154945/https://gadgetwise.blogs.nytimes.com/2010/01/27/digital-help-for-haiti/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="forbes">{{cite news |title=Technology Saves Lives In Haiti |first=Brady |last=Forrest |url=http://www.forbes.com/2010/02/01/text-messages-maps-technology-breakthroughs-haiti.html |newspaper=[[Forbes|Forbes]].com |date=2010-02-01 |accessdate=2014-12-12 |language=en |archive-date=2021-02-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210204231541/https://www.forbes.com/2010/02/01/text-messages-maps-technology-breakthroughs-haiti.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

在海地地圖繪製完成後，不少世界各地的組織開始使用OSM的海地地圖來進行援助工作，這些組織有世界銀行，歐洲聯合佣金研究中心，聯合國指揮部，聯合國救援隊等其他組織。<ref>{{cite web | last = Turner | first = Andrew | title = World Bank Haiti Situation Room – featuring OSM | date = 2010-02-03 | url = https://secure.flickr.com/photos/ajturner/4329833289/in/photostream/ | language = en | accessdate = 2014-12-12 | archive-date = 2019-07-12 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190712235730/https://secure.flickr.com/photos/ajturner/4329833289/in/photostream/ | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | first = European Commission Joint Research Centre | title = Haiti Earthquakes: Infrastructure Port-au-Prince 15/01/2010 | date = 2010-01-15 | url = http://ec.europa.eu/dgs/jrc/downloads/jrc_pp_haiti_map_04.pdf | format = PDF | language = en | accessdate = 2014-12-12 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121025082950/http://ec.europa.eu/dgs/jrc/downloads/jrc_pp_haiti_map_04.pdf | archivedate = 2012-10-25 }}</ref><ref name="pbatty_video">{{cite web | last = Batty | first = Peter | title = OpenStreetMap in Haiti – video | date = 2010-02-14 | url = http://geothought.blogspot.com/2010/02/openstreetmap-in-haiti-video.html | accessdate = 2014-12-12 | language = en | archive-date = 2010-02-18 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20100218143227/http://geothought.blogspot.com/2010/02/openstreetmap-in-haiti-video.html | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="osm-wiki-haiti">{{cite web |url=https://wiki.openstreetmap.org/wiki/WikiProject_Haiti |title=WikiProject Haiti |work=OpenStreetMap Wiki |accessdate=2010-02-05 |language=en |archive-date=2012-06-02 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/687n94uJg?url=http://wiki.openstreetmap.org/wiki/WikiProject_Haiti |dead-url=no }}</ref>

OSM人道主義團隊（[[openstreetmap:Humanitarian_OSM_Team|Humanitarian OpenStreetMap Team]]）也和類似非政府組織救災隊（USAID等）合作，從幾乎空白的OSM地圖開始標記海地和其他國家的區域，幫助原先地圖是甚麼都沒有的地區建立圖資。<ref>{{cite web |title=OSM Marks the SpotHaitians use a crowdsourced map to chart their own country, and its development |url=https://medium.com/medium-for-haiti/f4582ed41656 |publisher=medium.com |access-date=2014-12-14 |archive-date=2013-10-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131014053722/https://medium.com/medium-for-haiti/f4582ed41656 |dead-url=no }}</ref>而各個組織同時也參與建設海地的避難營。

在海地災情過後，OSM也在後來的發生災難的地區產生了重大的作用，例如，馬利（2013年1月）<ref>{{cite web|title=OSM 2012 Mali Crisis wiki page|url=http://wiki.openstreetmap.org/wiki/2012_Mali_Crisis|accessdate=2014-12-12|language=en|archive-date=2021-03-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210330000345/https://wiki.openstreetmap.org/wiki/2012_Mali_Crisis|dead-url=no}}</ref>，菲律賓的海燕（2013年11月）<ref>{{cite web|first=New Scientist|title=Social media helps aid efforts after typhoon Haiyan|url=http://www.newscientist.com/article/dn24565-social-media-helps-aid-efforts-after-typhoon-haiyan.html#.U-QaA2MmUro|date=November 12, 2013|accessdate=2014-12-12|language=en|archive-date=2015-04-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150416222050/http://www.newscientist.com/article/dn24565-social-media-helps-aid-efforts-after-typhoon-haiyan.html#.U-QaA2MmUro|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|first=The Atlantic|title=How Online Mapmakers Are Helping the Red Cross Save Lives in the Philippines|url=http://www.theatlantic.com/technology/archive/2013/11/how-online-mapmakers-are-helping-the-red-cross-save-lives-in-the-philippines/281366/|date=2013-11-12|accessdate=2014-12-12|language=en|archive-date=2021-04-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210421175915/https://www.theatlantic.com/technology/archive/2013/11/how-online-mapmakers-are-helping-the-red-cross-save-lives-in-the-philippines/281366/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，還有西非的伊波拉（2014年3月）<ref>{{cite web|first=Nuviun|title=How the Internet is Stopping the Ebola Outbreak, One Street Map at a Time|url=http://nuviun.com/content/blog/How-the-Internet-is-Stopping-the-Ebola-Outbreak-One-Street-Map-at-a-Time|accessdate=2014-12-12|language=en|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141019042927/http://nuviun.com/content/blog/How-the-Internet-is-Stopping-the-Ebola-Outbreak-One-Street-Map-at-a-Time|archive-date=2014-10-19|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，再次顯現了各個不同的國際組織即使通過互聯網，也能從標記OSM地圖中來幫助人道主義組織進行援助。

